_aChangeLog.text: Redesigned certain stages to make speedrunning easier
Fixed the fan in the sewer

_sText:
This is my first non-simplistic map that I have made, please enjoy.	
This map was made in about **3 days** since I recieved many comments on previous maps about using real textures and not flat ones, which I have now done so.		

Difficulty: Medium - Hard	
Length: Long		

All feedback is welcome, I hope you enjoy!		

Note: The Sewer (2nd area) was made a long time ago, which I decided to use now in this map, please excuse how ugly it may look / poorly optimized it is.
